name: LemonGuard
categories:
NA,  The lemon guards are Lemon People who guard the entrance to Castle Lemongrab. There seem to be only 2 of them and they dont seem to currently have any weapons. They had a shield each. They were created along the first Lemon People, as seen in All Your Fault.

==Appearance==
They wear white uniforms and white hats with lemons depicted on the hats. The second guards hat has an extension on top of it. The first guard has big ears, a medium long nose and a grin shaped like half a lemon, while the second has no ears, no nose and doesnt smile.

==Duties==
They only stay on stools and get up whenever they need to do their duties. One sits in a cabin and the other sits outside. Their only known duty is to close and open the doors leading to the castle.

name: Leviathan
categories:
NA, Leviathan was a whale that appeared in the episode "Billys Bucket List".  In the episode, Finn knocks himself out with a wooden board so he can overcome his fear of Ocean|the ocean.  Because of knocking himself unconscious, he has a strange dream where Leviathan appears and steals Finns hat|his hat by biting its "ear" and pulling it off.  At the end of the dream, Leviathan eats him, leading to Finn being woken up by Fear Feaster|the Fear Feaster.

==Appearance==
Leviathan appears as a normal whale, but with, apparently, no eyes.  Its skin is a dark shade of blue on the top, and a lighter shade on its underside.  However, towards the end of Finns dream, Leviathan appears purple.  Leviathan also has sharp teeth, unlike some whales, allowing it to eat Finn easily.

==Trivia==
*Leviathans name was most likely inspired by http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Leviathan the biblical creature of the same name.
